{"tid":2068994,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"觀塘區好食金黃黃食店執笠，希望執前大家支持吓","createTime":"2020-06-18T05:41:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-20T04:07:21.000Z","uid":71283,"like":39,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"4d601f5327f41eebb666c3f01b3eaaca0b8d612a","tid":2068994,"uid":71283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T05:41:30.000Z","msg":"呢間嘢賣泰式船麵，之前有frd介紹食過幾次，係極好味！所以我之後都有介紹朋友去呢間試吓，個個都讚不絕口，湯濃麵彈！<br />\n之後喺其他香港地方都食唔返咁好味嘅船麵<br />\n但今日突然喺facebook見到佢話要執啦，做到下個月中就收皮。雖然米已成炊，但都希望各位觀塘區手足有機會可以試吓，比個支持老細。<br />\n至於佢有幾黃，我就唔特別多講啦，基本上罷工罷足，個個post都會屌政府咁，你去佢fb睇吓就知。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NHHswHy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNHHswHy.png&h=d6e01cc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mMDfFBg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmMDfFBg.jpg&h=a6d29f4f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"36c69efb016f8e13daac169fb5c6a921f7af4f6b","tid":2068994,"uid":71283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T05:43:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/captain.thai.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcaptain.thai.hk&d=u0uYB5UElWTGJsHKTdw4wfUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=3a5449ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/captain.thai.hk</a><br />\n補返條fb link，大家可以入去睇吓"},{"pid":"8db0b5b258d651aea98a501e0f7577f9d8fd0bb4","tid":2068994,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T05:45:43.000Z","msg":"有食過幾好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56f86f81e35711aeac78fcc453b588fed20e92d3","tid":2068994,"uid":62721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T05:46:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0523358448e4dbf9868e4f4feb09cd763b95bc9b","tid":2068994,"uid":71283,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"8db0b5b258d651aea98